### 11. Test 404 behavior for non-existing Participant ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/model/raceparticipant/complex/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

> {%
    client.test("Request with dummy ID should return 404 NotFound", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 404, "Expected HTTP 404 NotFound");
    });
%}